body_html: @petewarden Mul and final_result are not the input and output names I used, but rather, the example usage given in the documentation. I included them just for the sake of illustration, but the actual command I used had the input and output node names I used in the java code as well. In fact, I think it would not be possible to run the graph transform tool successfully if the node names are invalid or do not exist within the graph. I think, at least for my use case, quantize_nodes somehow gave me the error when running.
